54
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:53,260
"Poopack"?
“普霸”？

55
00:03:55,960 --> 00:04:00,260
Yeah. All right. Well, that rules out Lana Titwyler.
好吧，没关系 那莱娜缇婉乐可能也不行了

56
00:04:04,810 --> 00:04:08,870
- I've got good news. - You got out of the whole Tulsa thing?
-我有好消息 -你不用去土尔沙了吗？

57
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:11,530
Okay, I have news.
好吧，我有新消息

58
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:15,610
